2009;;I Hate Valentine's Day;;American;;Nia Vardalos;;Nia Vardalos, John Corbett;;romantic comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/I_Hate_Valentine%27s_Day;;Florist Genevieve Gernier (Vardalos) believes that the best way to achieve romantic fulfillment is to never go on more than five dates with the same man. She is forced to reassess her philosophy when she meets Greg Gatlin (Corbett), a restaurateur who moves into her neighborhood.